      • addSongToPlaylist

        public java.lang.String addSongToPlaylist​(int pListIndex,
                                          int nameIndex,
                                          java.lang.String user,
                                          int choose)
        Method: addSongToPlaylist
        this method add song to a playlist and update the duration
        pre: the array poolOfSongs[] must be different of null , poolOfSongs[] !=null pos: A song is added to the array songs[], which belongs to the class Playlist, and the duration of the playlist is set
        Parameters:
        pListIndex - , the position of the playlist that the user chose
        nameIndex - , the position of the song that the user chose
        user - , the name of the user for checking is the user has access to the playlist
        choose - , it represents the type of playlist chosen by the user
        Returns:
        String, telling if the user added the song to the playlist or a message where it says that the user does not have access to that playlist
